Package editor.mapEditor

Class Summary
DrawCanvas the canvas used by the map editor to draw the world and to handel the mouse events of placing elements into the world
MapEditor edits map files for use in the game
SelectionPanel the panel that selects the element that will be added to the world by dragging the mouse in the editor
